{
  "stem": "7437.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I can blame it on that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the late spring of 1942, rumors began to fly in the ghetto that something was up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We really didn't know-- I say we.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But my mother would come home with different stories.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And everyone was getting very apprehensive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was something going on, but we didn't sense what.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We knew it wasn't anything good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My mother desperately tried, while she was working outside building roads and digging ditches, to find a place where she-- we could hide for the rest of the war.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she finally was successful in obtaining two places.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She could not get one place for the three of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Nobody, you know, would hide three people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so one evening, she and my sister came back from work ecstatic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She did locate two farmers who were willing to take us into hiding.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "By that time, we knew something was coming and not very-- in the not very distant future.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The German guards increased immeasurably.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there was a lot-- a lot of traffic in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And everybody sensed that something was happening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And everybody tried either to find a hiding place or naively, they built partitions in their little rooms, thinking they could hide there and the Germans wouldn't find them.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I even remember in one of the neighboring houses, a man was trying to find-- build a hiding place in a chimney, you know, which was so unrealistic.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But, you know, everyone clings to hope.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Well, one day, early-- I guess it was summer by then-- my terrific big sister was getting ready to go to work.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We hugged.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
